msgid "|image1384|"
msgstr "|image1384|"

#: ../../source/tools.rst:2776
msgid "You can customize the columns of this table in the :ref:`'Table settings'<column-settings-label>` section of the Administration module (table id: stock_rotation_manage_items)."
msgstr ""
"Sie können die Spalten dieser Tabelle über die ref:`Tabellenkonfiguration "
